# Mini App: Daily Card Vending


## Prereqs
- Node 18+
- pnpm or npm
- Wallet funded on **Base mainnet** for prod (use **Base Sepolia** for testing)


## Install
pnpm i
cd web && pnpm i


## Deploy contracts (choose network)
# Testnet
# pnpm hardhat run scripts/deploy.ts --network baseSepolia
# Mainnet
# pnpm hardhat run scripts/deploy.ts --network base


## Configure VRF (Base mainnet)
- Create a VRF **subscription** on Base, note the sub ID
- Fund the subscription with **LINK on Base** (token address in `.env`)
- Set `VRF_COORDINATOR`, `VRF_KEYHASH` (30 gwei lane recommended), and `VRF_SUBSCRIPTION_ID`
- Add your **VendingMachine** contract as a consumer for the subscription


## Run web
cd web && pnpm dev


## Notes
- Base Mainnet chainId: **8453**; explorer: basescan.org
- Update `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` with deployed addresses.
